vodQA is a conference by ThoughtWorks for Quality Enthusiasts. In it's 2015 edition at Bengaluru, I conducted a workshop on DevOps 101 with a team, which talked about the below topics.

Workshop Topics
---------------
1. Intro to DevOps and Infrastructure As Code
2. Virtualization and Vagrant
3. Configuration Management
4. Hands-on Configuration Management with Puppet

The video of the workshop can be found [here](https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=DevOps+101) and the slides [here](http://www.slideshare.net/ThoughtWorks/dev-ops-101). I wrote a [blog post](http://www.thoughtworks.com/insights/blog/five-box-workshop) on the same in ThoughtWorks Insights blog.
